Magmatron:

     "Not quite yet," The Destron commander said. "But I might need 
everybody soon, we may be attacking."
     He liked the fact that everybody was being so recptive, but he 
also didn't trust them, his suspicous nature made him belive that 
they would backstab him. But the Destrons are not the Predacons, they 
have more honor than that.
